Emil - Play Heroes of the Storm Free Now—Earn the Heroes of the Storm Card Back in Hearthstone!

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*****************************************************************************

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Greetings Emil,

Calling all heroes! The portal to the Nexus is open and ready for you to storm the Battlegrounds—Heroes of the Storm™, Blizzard Entertainment’s free-to-play online team brawler, is now available for Windows and Mac! Join your friends and bash through forts, brawl with Grave Golems, and go toe-to-toe against other teams of Warcraft®, StarCraft®, and Diablo® Heroes as you fight for victory!  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

PLAY FREE NOW
> http://eu.battle.net/heroes/
  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
As an added bonus, enter the fray during the week of June 2 and you’ll receive an exclusive portrait to commemorate the game’s launch.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
COLLECT THE HEROES OF THE STORM CARD BACK
Battle in the Nexus, earn rewards at the Inn! When you achieve Player Level 12 in Heroes of the Storm, you’ll unlock the new Heroes of the Storm card back in Hearthstone®.   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
PLAY AS POWERFUL HEROES
Jump into the brawl as one of more than 35 playable Heroes from across Blizzard’s game universes, including Uther, Jaina, and Malfurion—with many more to come.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
MASTER THE BATTLEGROUNDS
Take a stand on one of 7 different battlegrounds, each with unique dynamic objectives that can turn the tide of the brawl.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
OTHER FEATURES
GAMEPLAY MODES:
Team up against computer-controlled opponents in Versus A.I. mode or test your mettle against human foes in Quick Match or highly competitive Ranked Play.

HERO SKINS:
Customize your Hero and defeat your opponents in style with over 130 skins, including Master Skins to unlock for each Hero.

HERO MOUNTS:
Charge into battle on one of over a dozen steadfast mounts—with more being added regularly.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Head over to the official Heroes of the Storm website to download the game for free on Windows and Mac, then grab some friends and join the fun!

See you in the Nexus!
- The Heroes of the Storm Team.  
